source: TEXT_CMNDEFTOMESTONEEXCHANGE_00153_HELP<tab>Seems every other day we stop dealing in this or that type of tomestone. Inevitably, there comes a point when Rowena says that they're not worth the hassle anymore.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFTOMESTONEEXCHANGE_00153_HELP<tab><var 2B ((<var 32 ((Item)) 06E802030202 /var>)) /var>? Die werden als Zahlungsmittel nicht mehr akzeptiert. Die Sammler scheinen das Interesse daran verloren zu haben.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFTOMESTONEEXCHANGE_00153_TALK_NOT_HAVE<tab>Might be as I still have use for them, though. If you have any you don't need, bring them here and I'll give you something more desirable in exchange.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFTOMESTONEEXCHANGE_00153_TALK_NOT_HAVE<tab>Ich könnte deine gegen <var 32 ((Item)) 06E803030502 /var> eintauschen ... wenn du welche besitzen würdest.
